Our Story

Built from a Simple Frustration

Poinciana Luxe Escapes was born from a simple observation: visiting Barbados shouldn’t mean juggling three different vendors for your car, your accommodation, and your experiences. Too many visitors spend their first day on the island stressed about logistics instead of soaking it in.

We created an integrated service that handles everything under one roof. One point of contact, one trusted team, one seamless experience from landing to departure. Because your time in Barbados should feel like a holiday from the very first moment.

Local Knowledge

Family-owned with deep roots in Barbados — the hidden spots, the best routes, the insider tips.

Personal Service

You’re not a booking number. You’re our guest, and we treat every stay like it’s personal.
